  <div class="stories-grid" id="stories-grid">
    <div class="story-card">
      <div class="story-img"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" loading="lazy" decoding="async" loading="lazy" decoding="async" loading="lazy" decoding="async" loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="images/img_124.jpg" alt="朱氏三厢房发源地"></div>
      <div class="story-body">
        <div class="story-title">朱氏三厢房发源地</div>
        <div class="story-date">1930-1940年代</div>
        <div class="story-desc">吾朱氏一脉，源溯沛国，源远流长。先祖忠厚立身，勤俭持家，以礼传家，以善待人。世代耕读为本，崇文尚德，尊老睦亲，邻里和睦。族人恪守祖训，明礼知义，安分守己，代代相传。今续修族谱，铭记先祖恩德，传承优良家风，愿后世子孙谨遵礼字辈分，修身立德，勤学上进，忠孝两全，团结族人，兴旺门第，光耀朱氏门庭。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="story-actions">
        <button class="btn btn-accent btn-sm" onclick="openStoryForm(2)">编辑</button>
        <button class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" onclick="deleteStory(2)">删除</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="story-card">
      <div class="story-img"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" loading="lazy" decoding="async" loading="lazy" decoding="async" loading="lazy" decoding="async" loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="images/img_125.jpg" alt="家庭团圆宴"></div>
      <div class="story-body">
        <div class="story-title">家庭团圆宴</div>
        <div class="story-date">2023年</div>
        <div class="story-desc">家庭成员首次大团圆，共叙家情，场面温馨感人。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="story-actions">
        <button class="btn btn-accent btn-sm" onclick="openStoryForm(3)">编辑</button>
        <button class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" onclick="deleteStory(3)">删除</button>
      </div>
    </div></div>
</div>

